<div class='post' itemprop='articleBody'>
<p>个人管理工业的必然后果就是私有制<br>
the management of industry by individuals necessarily implies private property</p>
</div>
<meta itemprop='headline' content='术语表 | 宣传语 | 成句'>
<div itemprop="interactionStatistic" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/InteractionCounter">
